    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234960/extras/503393ad6e9e2fcc60fa548c01f6d883.avif?t=1702962541\" width=600 height=260 /></span><br><br>Pygmalion是一款利用颜色合成的益智游戏。<br><br>通过让方块相互碰撞来清空舞台。<br><br>在一定的次数内清除所有方块，即可通关。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234960/extras/bdf7e9ccd9b3672f883af7ee7fcd48fa.poster.avif?t=1702962541\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234960/extras/bdf7e9ccd9b3672f883af7ee7fcd48fa.webm?t=1702962541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234960/extras/bdf7e9ccd9b3672f883af7ee7fcd48fa.mp4?t=1702962541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>简单的规则，但谜题并不容易</strong><br><br>通过限制方块移动次数来增加难度，让玩家在解决谜题时获得成就感。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234960/extras/f801b218c9abb7b9816df610f4ae6cc4.poster.avif?t=1702962541\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234960/extras/f801b218c9abb7b9816df610f4ae6cc4.webm?t=1702962541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234960/extras/f801b218c9abb7b9816df610f4ae6cc4.mp4?t=1702962541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234960/extras/14c6283047123179433da65e984be1bb.poster.avif?t=1702962541\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234960/extras/14c6283047123179433da65e984be1bb.webm?t=1702962541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234960/extras/14c6283047123179433da65e984be1bb.mp4?t=1702962541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>利用颜色特性创建的谜题关卡，可以通过合成和分离各种颜色来感受每个关卡的新体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2234960/extras/ee4247b1c6661a04e4f2cdc30c4e4412.avif?t=1702962541\" width=600 height=270 /></span><br><br><strong>谜题与视觉小说的结合</strong><br><br>Pygmalion通过将颜色和情感作为谜题的主题，创造了一个连贯的故事情节。<br><br>研究带有情感的机器人的概念是为每个关卡制作的一个短篇故事。",
